        "text": "Experiments with two mVLMs on three downstream tasks show that SUF brings consistent gains in ZS-XLT, especially for visual Q&A (xGQA) by up to 10 points, and the fact that in multilingual models these representations encode higher-level semantics rather than low-level language-specific idiosyncrasies should render SUF beneficial for ZS-XLT."
